metadata.name: Let's make a deal
metadata.description:
*"Please allow me to introduce myself*
*I'm a man of wealth and taste*
*I've been around for a long, long years*
*Stole million man's soul and faith"*

 *~ Mick Jagger*


we all make deals in one way or another though some can be more tempting than others. there are some that say i may have made a deal with the devil and that is how i produce the art that i create, that may or may not be true, but one thing is certain...he has become a part of my self

this is a part of a continuing series around my Devil persona that is a very personal project and is a huge part of who i am

the full story behind this persona can be read here: 

[How it began](https://twitter.com/Godriguezart/status/1457735392036376586)

[The image that started it all](https://foundation.app/@godriguezart/foundation/43334)
